The paper deals with unsupervised image-to-image translation, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed framework is based on Coupled GANs, which is a type of generative model and falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses domain adaptation, which is a topic that falls under graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
